            opportunities, and discussing new technologies. Feel free to reach
            out through any of these channels:
          </p>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <a
              href="https://twitter.com/murapadev"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="flex items-center p-4 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200 bg-white/90 dark:bg-neutral-900/90 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 hover:text-blue-500 dark:hover:text-blue-400 border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700"
            >
              <div
                class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center text-xl bg-blue-400/10 dark:bg-blue-600/10 text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 rounded-full"
              >
                ùïè
              </div>
              <div class="ml-4">
                <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                  Twitter
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                  @murapadev
                </p>
              </div>
            </a>

            <a
              href="mailto:murapabytes@gmail.com"
              class="flex items-center p-4 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200 bg-white/90 dark:bg-neutral-900/90 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 hover:text-red-500 dark:hover:text-red-400 border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700"
            >
              <div
                class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center text-xl bg-red-400/10 dark:bg-red-600/10 text-red-500 dark:text-red-400 rounded-full"
